# Code Qualiy

- Use TDD always
- Before making any edits run the following commands to get context: npm test -- --watchAll=false; npm run cypress:run; and npm run build;
- After making any edits run the following commands to verify you didnt break anything: npm test -- --watchAll=false; npm run cypress:run; and npm run build;
- when everything is ok run: npm run lint and npm run format and fix any warnings or errors in the process
- then run build, and tests after the last modification before saying success.